### Setting proxy for git in windows as well as in ubuntu OS

Command to use:

`git config --global http.proxy http://proxyuser:proxypwd@proxyServer:3128`

    change proxyuser to your proxy user  
    change proxypwd to your proxy password  
    change proxyServer to the URL of your proxy server  
    change 3128 to the proxy port configured on your proxy server  


If you decide at any time to reset this proxy and work without proxy:

Command to use:

`git config --global --unset http.proxy`

Finally, to check the currently set proxy:

`git config --global --get http.proxy`

